H^2-K=\frac{(R + 2r\cos(u))^2}{r^2(R + r\cos(u))^2}-\frac{\cos(u)}{r(R + r\cos(u))}=\frac{\frac{R^2}{4}+3(\frac{R}{2}+r\cos(u))^2}{r^2(R + r\cos(u))^2}>0.
